Detailed Description

RPC flavor is represented by a 32 bits integer.

Currently the high 12 bits are unused, must be set to 0 for future expansion. 

 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | 4b (bulk svc) | 4b (bulk type) | 4b (svc) | 4b (mech)  | 4b (policy) |
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
